cs.RO, cs.MA, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on the deployment of mobile robots to establish communication links between two previously disconnected sites. This falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of self-organisation and emergence in artificial life, which is related to multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and systems and control (cs.SY). The use of neuroevolution for one of the heuristics also falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
